text: Watermael-Boitsfort (in French) or Watermaal-Bosvoorde (in Dutch) is a municipality in the south of the city of Brussels in Belgium. In 2007, 24121 people lived there. It is at 50° 48 North, 04° 24 East. ==References== Category:Municipalities of Brussels-Capital Region
title: Watermael-Boitsfort
